Sat Jun 21 12:00:00 UTC 2026 - Juan Manuel Méndez Rey <juan.mendezr@proton.me>

- Initial openSUSE package (version 1.6.5).
  xwpe is the revived Borland-style console/X11 IDE: a single binary
  (wpe/we console, xwpe/xwe X11) with a syntax-highlighting editor,
  project management, multi-language compiler integration and
  source-level debugging (gdb/jdb/pdb), plus LSP and DAP clients.
  New upstream at https://codeberg.org/mendezr/xwpe ; Debian sid already
  tracks this fork.
